attributes.title: Chapter 1- the meeting üôÄ
attributes.review:
*3am at the park*
Me: ugh I‚Äôm so tired and I have nothing to do I should have stayed home (gets up and starts to walk home)

-noise behind the bush-
Me: huh? [confused] what was that? 
-noise comes closer- 
Me: WHO IS THERE
-phone starts going crazy and opens the App Store-
Me: WHAT THE...?
-downloads this app-
Me: trump 2020 app?[confused not knowing what was happening and not knowing what to do at the moment I opened the app]
-she hesitated-
Me: sigh ok let‚Äôs see what this is about...
-shows picture of an orange Cheeto-
Me: AHHHH [i screamed as the picture of the malignant Cheeto stood on my screen it was like I was being watched... I didn‚Äôt feel safe I knew I had to leave and delete this but how could I? The Cheeto or also known as the mafia leader had been in power for 4 years and how could I a normal citizen stand up before all the evil and malignant forces he was giving me? So then my journey began...]

*the next morning*
Me: [i decided to leave it alone for now and wait till morning to take action... I was so scared and frightened at the moment and I didn‚Äôt know what else to do so I opened my phone and got inside the App Store for so it was time to give this evil spawn app an end.]

*30min before*
Me: [i scrolled down the best app in this world when I noticed that it wasn‚Äôt only my issue but other people had also been through my same trauma... I sighed and decided to follow their orders...]

*present*
Me: it‚Äôs time [it was time to rate the app 1 Star out of 5 and share my very traumatic experience with the world for everyone who was harrassed by this Cheeto]

The end :)
